<ArticleH3 articleH3Text="Discover  berlin's outdoor dance spots" />

<ArticleParagraph
  articlePText={`Why just see the city when you can dance through it? Berlin's outdoor dance scene turns sightseeing into a full-body experience. From swing to salsa, tango to waltz, you'll find dancers gathering by the Spree and in leafy parks all summer long. And the best part? Many of these events are free.`}
/>

<ArticleParagraph
  articlePText={`Monbijoupark - Dance Under the Stars
Right by the Bode Museum, Monbijoupark transforms into one of Berlin's most magical open-air dance floors. The park's beach bar hosts daily sessions with everything from swing and waltz to salsa and tango.`}
/>
<ArticleLink 
linkUrl = "https://www.visitberlin.de/en/event/dance-monbijou-park" linkText ="Click here for more info"
/>


