<ArticleParagraph
articlePText={`Paul-Löbe-Haus - Tango by the River
Just across from the Reichstag, dancers gather almost every evening in summer to practice tango in front of Paul-Löbe-Haus. It's relaxed, social, and free—perfect whether you're a beginner looking to pick up your first steps or someone already hooked on tango's rhythm.`}
/>
